lead_paragraph: AMSTERDAM (via Berlin) Oct. 1 -- The Bourse was less active and prices easier. Royal Dutch dropped 614 points to 318; Amsterdam Rubber 6 1/2 to 478 1/2; Amsterdam Trading 2 1/2 to 312 1/2; Philips 4 to 267 1/4; Unilever 1 1/2 to 162 7/8 and A.K.U. 1 to 142 1/8.
